{"tid":1208504,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十幾萬人都對付唔到嗰百幾個警察， 算唔算國際笑話","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:36:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:11:52.000Z","uid":43785,"like":12,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"276bcc67b7151f3c4f5edb58aa8fe652f8267ac4","tid":1208504,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:36:53.000Z","msg":"如題：十幾萬人都對付唔到嗰百幾個警察，算唔算國際笑話。<br />\n<br />\n外國果邊玩得好激，我當然唔想大家搞成咁，但依家咁樣唔拖唔水食子彈，真係俾人笑成世。<br />\n<br />\n你哋班香港人..... <br />\n一隊警察有時得十零廿個人， <br />\n網上口口聲聲講到話開戰， <br />\n我唔信嗰廿個人過十萬人都搞佢唔掂。<br />\n佢哋係唔係一個頂一千個咁勁呀？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n分散曬企嘅時候唔做衝擊， <br />\n係都要等人哋聚埋一齊嘅時候先嚟沖擊。<br />\n外國嗰邊望住香港恥笑緊， 你哋知唔知呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港抗爭，真係國際笑話。<br />\n我勸你哋都係返屋企玩泥沙啦， 唔好同政府對抗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇本事既，真心唔想你地傷晒，回家啦。"},{"pid":"0f51956a88d00e033236b532beeb5eb1dd33eb07","tid":1208504,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"與其搞國際笑話，不如留力，不要受傷，仲有成個星期呀"},{"pid":"a026bad992991966c03067e18701b86f3fc90244","tid":1208504,"uid":43785,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:48:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61052aa2976a48518cf6c930751c0145742e324","tid":1208504,"uid":158404,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:52:28.000Z","msg":"話香港人太和平無用係偽命題<br />\n香港人無受過軍訓等等等 <br />\n咪再講埋啲on9野 <br />\n咁呢家係唔work 嘛 <br />\n你沖過去擋子彈囉"},{"pid":"9de7865512dcc0e79ee8d4d88d8bc48e26123ca5","tid":1208504,"uid":57566,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T18:52:36.000Z","msg":"人地升級 我地都要進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今次唔識處理催淚彈<br />\n下次我地就會識再用水淋<br />\n今次冇裝備防子彈<br />\n我們聽日就整甲！<br />\n唔好輸啊香港人！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7333c34ff7e877b25fc93784b00f089f326c42a5","tid":1208504,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:04:18.000Z","msg":"進化我地就輸。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6558d9301e29a293cee7b4b59e050c56cf7ec4e9","tid":1208504,"uid":69314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:07:43.000Z","msg":"大家有共識行動，請幫手推下，share出去<br />\n<br />\n613行動部署<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1212252\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1212252</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cc1495b620f087f360544a6e9137855ef7a86fda","tid":1208504,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7333c34ff7e877b25fc93784b00f089f326c42a5","tid":1208504,"uid":117600,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T19:04:18.000Z","msg":"進化我地就輸。。。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:11:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}